              <div class="faq-content">
                <h4>Can I generate PDFs from the platform?</h4>
                <p>
                  Yes, PDF generation (CVs, contracts, summaries) is provided via KnpSnappy and wkhtmltopdf.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="col-lg-6">
            <div class="single-faq wow fadeInUp" data-wow-delay=".1s">
              <div class="faq-icon">
                <i class="lni lni-question-circle"></i>
              </div>
              <div class="faq-content">
                <h4>How does CV parsing work?</h4>
                <p>
                  Using smalot/pdfparser, the platform automatically extracts key information from PDF resumes to streamline applicant analysis.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="single-faq wow fadeInUp" data-wow-delay=".15s">
              <div class="faq-icon">
                <i class="lni lni-question-circle"></i>
              </div>
              <div class="faq-content">
                <h4>Does the platform include an HR calendar?</h4>
                <p>
                  Yes, Tattali CalendarBundle integration allows HR teams to schedule meetings, interviews, and manage availability.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="single-faq wow fadeInUp" data-wow-delay=".2s">
              <div class="faq-icon">
                <i class="lni lni-question-circle"></i>
              </div>
              <div class="faq-content">
                <h4>What AI features are available?</h4>
                <p>
                  Career Bridge enables automatic generation of HR texts, profile analysis, and is ready for more advanced AI-powered features via OpenAI.
                </p>
              </div>
